<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 12:11:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拜登表示以色列已准备好暂停加沙战斗；哈马斯称协议尚未完成</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/biden-says-israel-is-ready-to-pause-gaza-fighting-hamas-says-deal-not-done-yet/0000018d-e991-d9a9-a1bd-ebbb67a00000</link><description>以色列代表团周一抵达卡塔尔继续会谈，美国总统乔·拜登在斋月之前公开设定下周在加沙达成停火协议的最后期限。然而，哈马斯否认已达成协议</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 11:36:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/biden-says-israel-is-ready-to-pause-gaza-fighting-hamas-says-deal-not-done-yet/0000018d-e991-d9a9-a1bd-ebbb67a00000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列不后悔自己从未支持乌克兰对抗俄罗斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/why-israel-isnt-sorry-it-never-stood-by-ukraine-against-russia/0000018d-e623-d7f4-a3dd-e62f0fdb0000</link><description>尽管俄罗斯加入了针对以色列的伊朗-哈马斯-真主党轴心，但以色列同意向乌克兰提供军事援助的可能性比以前更小了</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 10:31:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/why-israel-isnt-sorry-it-never-stood-by-ukraine-against-russia/0000018d-e623-d7f4-a3dd-e62f0fdb0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡为何缺席以色列地方选举活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/why-netanyahu-is-absent-from-israels-local-election-campaigns/0000018d-e982-d1e0-a1dd-f9f79b810000</link><description>在国家层面上，地方选举很少能表明政治风向，尤其是在今年预计投票率异常低的情况下。但在战争期间举行选举仍然是以色列民主的一项成就</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 10:15:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/why-netanyahu-is-absent-from-israels-local-election-campaigns/0000018d-e982-d1e0-a1dd-f9f79b810000</guid></item><item><title>由于公众冷漠和加沙战争拖延，以色列人在地方选举中投票</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israelis-to-vote-in-local-elections-amid-public-apathy-and-gaza-war-delay/0000018d-e73c-db28-afdf-fffc64e00000</link><description>投票站早上 7 点开放，晚上 10 点关闭 ■ 预计投票率较低 ■ 由于缺席选票较多，最终结果将在选举后约五天左右公布 ■ 战斗中的以色列士兵将在加沙境内投票条</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 04:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israelis-to-vote-in-local-elections-amid-public-apathy-and-gaza-war-delay/0000018d-e73c-db28-afdf-fffc64e00000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列北部发射火箭后，以色列国防军袭击了黎巴嫩的军事基地；卡塔尔对人质协议持“乐观”态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-live/biden-sets-march-4-target-for-gaza-truce-mossad-chief-delaying-aid-risks-hostage-deal/0000018d-e888-d1e0-a1dd-f9fd39400000</link><description>拜登表示，他希望加沙在下周之前停火 ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部称，昨天加沙有 96 人死亡 ■ 消息人士称，哈马斯正在研究涉及 40 天停火和交换人质的巴黎休战提案 ■ 以色列国防军在加沙杀死了三名武装巴勒斯坦人约旦河西岸 ■ 巴勒斯坦总理提交辞职，将领导巴勒斯坦权力机构过渡政府</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 03:13:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article-live/biden-sets-march-4-target-for-gaza-truce-mossad-chief-delaying-aid-risks-hostage-deal/0000018d-e888-d1e0-a1dd-f9fd39400000</guid></item><item><title>辛贝特警告犯罪分子已渗透到以色列-阿拉伯理事会，建议推迟地方选举</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-warns-criminal-gangs-have-infiltrated-israeli-arab-councils/0000018d-e7e3-d7f4-a3dd-e7efd89e0000</link><description>发给内政部的秘密文件称，犯罪团伙在七个城市占据要职，并警告他们可能获得大量武器和爆炸物</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 00:26:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-warns-criminal-gangs-have-infiltrated-israeli-arab-councils/0000018d-e7e3-d7f4-a3dd-e7efd89e0000</guid></item><item><title>右翼非政府组织向巴勒斯坦活动人士道歉，称其与恐怖分子住在同一所房子里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/rightist-ngo-to-apologize-to-palestinian-activist-for-saying-he-lived-in-terrorists-home/0000018d-e7be-d05b-addd-e7bfe4190000</link><description>Ad Kan 在 Facebook 上谎称伊萨·阿姆罗是 2001 年谋杀以色列婴儿 Shalhevet Pass 的男子的亲戚</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 23:45:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/rightist-ngo-to-apologize-to-palestinian-activist-for-saying-he-lived-in-terrorists-home/0000018d-e7be-d05b-addd-e7bfe4190000</guid></item><item><title>以色列证实：国家支付内塔尼亚胡私人游泳池的战时维修费用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-confirms-state-paid-for-war-time-repairs-on-netanyahus-private-swimming-pool/0000018d-e73b-db28-afdf-fffbcce80000</link><description>在《国土报》发表报道后，总理办公室的法律顾问写道，部分修复工作已经完成，而其他请求则被审计长拒绝——审计长已辞职</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 23:10:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-confirms-state-paid-for-war-time-repairs-on-netanyahus-private-swimming-pool/0000018d-e73b-db28-afdf-fffbcce80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列央行维持利率在4.5%不变，理由是加沙战争持续存在不确定性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/bank-of-israel-holds-interest-rate-unchanged-at-4-5-citing-uncertainty-amid-gaza-war/0000018d-e6fe-d7f4-a3dd-e6fead2e0000</link><description>1 月份通货膨胀率年率降至 2.6%，为两年来最低。以色列央行行长表示，当我们看到通胀似乎趋于稳定时，我们将能够继续降低利率，理由是加沙战争的高度不确定性</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 20:37:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/bank-of-israel-holds-interest-rate-unchanged-at-4-5-citing-uncertainty-amid-gaza-war/0000018d-e6fe-d7f4-a3dd-e6fead2e0000</guid></item><item><title>数千名艺术家和策展人签署的请愿书旨在将以色列排除在威尼斯双年展之外</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/petition-signed-by-thousands-of-artists-aims-to-exclude-israel-from-venice-biennale/0000018d-e615-d47b-a1af-fe77a7600000</link><description>在致国际艺术展的一封公开信中，签署者呼吁“不要设立种族灭绝馆”，并声称计划中的以色列展览代表了一个“对巴勒斯坦人实施暴行”的国家</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 19:33:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/petition-signed-by-thousands-of-artists-aims-to-exclude-israel-from-venice-biennale/0000018d-e615-d47b-a1af-fe77a7600000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡承认，与之前的否认相反，他只知道哈马斯在 10 月 7 日激活了“少数”以色列 SIM 卡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-admits-knowing-of-few-sim-cards-activated-in-gaza-on-oct-7-contrary-to-denial/0000018d-e655-d47b-a1af-fe776a790000</link><description>总理办公室否认内塔尼亚胡知道哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击的迹象，但两名高级国防官员告诉《国土报》，内塔尼亚胡在战争的头几天参与了有关此事的讨论。随后总理承认“10 月 7 日之后”听取了该问题</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 18:28:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-admits-knowing-of-few-sim-cards-activated-in-gaza-on-oct-7-contrary-to-denial/0000018d-e655-d47b-a1af-fe776a790000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 143 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-143/0000018d-e680-d47b-a1af-fef657660000</link><description>以色列代表团抵达卡塔尔参加人质释放协议谈判 ■ 以色列战时内阁批准援助直接进入加沙北部 ■ 以色列国防军表示，它在加沙地带找到了约 10 公里长的隧道系统 ■ 以色列未能遵守国际法院向加沙人提供援助的命令, 人权观察称 ■ 以色列国防军称真主党东部指挥部负责人 ■ 战争结束 143 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 17:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-143/0000018d-e680-d47b-a1af-fef657660000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列电视上，如果你胆敢提及占领，你就是反犹太主义者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-26/ty-article/.highlight/on-israeli-tv-youre-an-antisemite-if-you-dare-mention-the-occupation/0000018d-e60c-de64-afff-f67f1cee0000</link><description>以色列纪录片导演尤瓦尔·亚伯拉罕周六在柏林国际电影节上发表的获奖感言《无他之地》被坎公共广播公司贴上了反犹太主义的标签。如今，任何提到事实的人都会被视为仇视犹太人</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 17:27:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-26/ty-article/.highlight/on-israeli-tv-youre-an-antisemite-if-you-dare-mention-the-occupation/0000018d-e60c-de64-afff-f67f1cee0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列情报机构在 10 月 7 日袭击发生前数小时检测到哈马斯激活的以色列 SIM 卡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-intel-detected-hundreds-of-israeli-sim-cards-activated-by-hamas-early-on-oct-7/0000018d-e5c3-dc4b-a1cd-f5efc8380000</link><description>这是异常活动的迹象，引发了高级国防官员在凌晨召开会议 ■ 普遍的评估称这是哈马斯演习 ■ 内塔尼亚胡办公室表示，以色列国防军称，以色列总理“直到现在才意识到这一点”卡在过去的事件中被激活</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 16:26:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-intel-detected-hundreds-of-israeli-sim-cards-activated-by-hamas-early-on-oct-7/0000018d-e5c3-dc4b-a1cd-f5efc8380000</guid></item><item><title>以色列向国际法院提交报告，详细说明加沙地带的行动不构成种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-submit-report-to-icj-detailing-actions-in-gaza-strip-do-not-constitute-genocide/0000018d-e5b9-dc4b-a1cd-f5bd616e0000</link><description>消息人士告诉《国土报》，以色列的报告主要涉及以色列正在履行对加沙人的人道主义义务并遵守法院在临时裁决中下令采取的临时措施的证据。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 15:23:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-submit-report-to-icj-detailing-actions-in-gaza-strip-do-not-constitute-genocide/0000018d-e5b9-dc4b-a1cd-f5bd616e0000</guid></item><item><title>当暴力主导阿以地方选举时，民主就会失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/when-violence-dominates-local-arab-israeli-elections-democracy-loses/0000018d-e52d-d596-a9ef-e7bf4ba20000</link><description>阿拉伯裔以色列公职人员越来越多地成为犯罪分子的目标，他们希望在周二的地方选举之前通过威胁、勒索和武力手段达到目的。竞选公职不应该让人们付出生命的代价</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 14:56:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/when-violence-dominates-local-arab-israeli-elections-democracy-loses/0000018d-e52d-d596-a9ef-e7bf4ba20000</guid></item><item><title>通过取消以色列奖，内塔尼亚胡的忠诚教育部长表现出了对更多的蔑视</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/by-canceling-israel-prize-netanyahus-education-minister-showed-contempt-for-much-more/0000018d-e516-d596-a9ef-e7b749400000</link><description>教育部长约夫·基什取消了今年的大部分奖项，因为其中一位获奖者领导了反政府抗议活动，将以色列奖变成了他自己的私人企业</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 12:10:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/by-canceling-israel-prize-netanyahus-education-minister-showed-contempt-for-much-more/0000018d-e516-d596-a9ef-e7b749400000</guid></item><item><title>禁令、强烈反对和销售：有关以色列和巴勒斯坦的书籍正在抢购一空</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/books-on-israel-palestine-are-flying-off-the-shelves-and-shaking-up-the-literary-world/0000018d-e034-d47b-a1af-fe76bae20000</link><description>一本关于一名巴勒斯坦男孩的书被从新泽西学区的课程中删除，以及纽约一家书店的以色列-巴勒斯坦角落引起了世界的关注，这只是关于以色列和巴勒斯坦的书籍如何震撼出版界的两个例子，自 10 月 7 日以来，新的对话浮出水面</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 10:09:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/books-on-israel-palestine-are-flying-off-the-shelves-and-shaking-up-the-literary-world/0000018d-e034-d47b-a1af-fe76bae20000</guid></item><item><title>加沙和以色列，一个新词联想游戏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/gaza-and-israel-a-new-word-association-game/0000018d-e0d2-df79-a5cd-e0fe41ef0000</link><description>广场上躺着他们的死者。令人印象深刻的战术成就。今天我们杀死了数十名恐怖分子。军队杀害了保护救援卡车免受抢劫的警察。它一直持续着</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 09:55:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/gaza-and-israel-a-new-word-association-game/0000018d-e0d2-df79-a5cd-e0fe41ef0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院命令国家澄清为何不招募犹太学院学生加入以色列国防军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-hears-draft-law-petitions-as-protesters-call-for-equal-service/0000018d-e46b-d7f4-a3dd-e66f39fc0000</link><description>前摩萨德负责人参加了请愿活动，呼吁招募极端正统派人士来服务，他表示“没有一个国家可以在不分担负担的情况下存在”</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 09:18:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-hears-draft-law-petitions-as-protesters-call-for-equal-service/0000018d-e46b-d7f4-a3dd-e66f39fc0000</guid></item></channel></rss>